item.title: CVE-2021-24407|2024-08-03T19:28:23.812Z -- tielabs -- jannah
item.description: The Jannah WordPress theme before 5.4.5 did not properly sanitize the 'query' POST parameter in its tie_ajax_search AJAX action, leading to a Reflected Cross-site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.

item.title: CVE-2021-24364|2024-08-03T19:28:24.012Z -- tielabs -- jannah
item.description: The Jannah WordPress theme before 5.4.4 did not properly sanitize the options JSON parameter in its tie_get_user_weather AJAX action before outputting it back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.
